---
import WorkDetail from '@pt/layouts/WorkDetail.astro'
---

<WorkDetail
  title="Newtopia"
  company="Tashi"
  period="2022 – 2023"
  role="QA Lead"
  category="Health & Wellness · iOS & Android"
  stack={['React Native', 'QA', 'iOS & Android']}
>
  <div class="mb-10">
    <p class="mb-4 font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest text-[#c9873a] uppercase">Overview</p>
    <p class="text-[15px] leading-[1.9] font-light text-white/60">
      Newtopia is a health and wellness app built with React Native, available on both iOS and Android. The app focuses
      on helping users build healthier habits through guided experiences and personalized wellness journeys.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10">
    <p class="mb-4 font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest text-[#c9873a] uppercase">My Role</p>
    <p class="mb-4 text-[15px] leading-[1.9] font-light text-white/60">
      As QA Lead at Tashi, I led a team of testers and made sure quality assurance was deeply embedded throughout the
      software lifecycle.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-4 space-y-3">
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <span class="mt-2 h-1 w-1 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#c9873a]"></span><p
          class="text-sm leading-relaxed font-light text-white/50"
        >
          Led and coordinated a team of QA testers across multiple release cycles.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <span class="mt-2 h-1 w-1 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#c9873a]"></span><p
          class="text-sm leading-relaxed font-light text-white/50"
        >
          Ensured quality assurance was integrated early in the development process, reducing late-stage bugs and
          rework.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <span class="mt-2 h-1 w-1 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#c9873a]"></span><p
          class="text-sm leading-relaxed font-light text-white/50"
        >
          Planned and managed test strategies aligned with product milestones and release schedules.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</WorkDetail>
